{"tid":1835014,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"重開！「行動下篇」「高鐵篇二亅","createTime":"2020-01-22T16:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T17:22:08.000Z","uid":199626,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ae4bfc0ac293a3a87048a6dd7128b63f9eeb55e7","tid":1835014,"uid":199626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"22號定23號？<br />\n「戰略 」迫使政府方全面封關不允許武漢人口進入<br />\n<br />\n「行動亅 使用魔法震懾帶菌者進入本港<br />\n或者高鐵無法運行/ 香港警方愛國愛港 駐守高鐵站 防止帶菌者硬闖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上述戰略目的以下開放討論及投票請放下其他貼文 謝謝大家！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持樓主<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主係鬼 叫人出去送頭 唔啦好攰 最多推一次就算啦 唔會爆一千 運動都收咗皮 有得啲五毛公關公司玩啦 黃之鋒行動前兩日推post唔使聽 大家一齊 貼文"},{"pid":"159d9457ff21e5565d2d2b298a989984cba442d0","tid":1835014,"uid":199626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:06:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"be895cfba6c59f9050c354c7d2e9c5e229b51e17","tid":1835014,"uid":199626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"91886703599293cc06af54f58c182707749375b0","tid":1835014,"uid":199626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"1676cc98d48441df9837b0c9a7123e616f45801f","tid":1835014,"uid":199626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e70f14b90585054eee313d5f939864f821286da5","tid":1835014,"uid":199626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"cab9a28f80fa75e0b9ad8e3aae453b6a173153ce","tid":1835014,"uid":199626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:08:45.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"7b09af588f896d9e12d52fa6d667092311e344e4","tid":1835014,"uid":208508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class