9da15cd0dde4c936b6f288dd91986dfa2","tid":1835014,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"24號最好，個個早收，要時間做文宣<br />\n<br />\n但團年飯麻煩"},{"pid":"dce74335ad6947b79b119a7bbe184ffb03d30bd8","tid":1835014,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">封站！封站！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">封站！封站！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">封站！封站！</span>"},{"pid":"2cf08e206aef3e9ac3a8677959637419de8e63a4","tid":1835014,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:22:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4440dc472687e4d728c1560eeb3a19b4a77e7635","tid":1835014,"uid":213246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa3ba579b0605b816a3f962ca4ef11d9c90cf94","tid":1835014,"uid":280886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:39:55.000Z","msg":"支持！到時仲可以大大力宣傳中共習近平D衰野，黑警千祁要保護內地同胞，唔好比佢地睇到！！<br />\n<br />\n(肺炎)港府唔限制大陸人來港，我地就令大陸政府限制佢地黎！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1834124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1834124</a><br />\n<br />\n部分患者只有低燒甚至無發燒症狀，邊境測體溫根本唔夠！要既係佢地唔好落黎！<br />\n<br />\nA. 方法：大陸政府最怕大陸人知道既，唔係香港點解抗爭（大陸已經洗曬地，而且大陸人唔care香港人點慘），而係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 高官好有錢（針對仇富心理）<br />\n<br />\n2. 高層全是外國勢力（針對民族主義）<br />\n<br />\n3. 習近平的情人們（針對八掛心理）<br />\n銅鑼灣書店事件係因此書觸怒習而起，雖然本書有點9up，但從事件可見，習真係好驚本書既內容見光<br />\n本書摘要：<a href=\"http://blog.udn.com/meatball2/47616636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.udn.com%2Fmeatball2%2F47616636&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=f15a154a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.udn.com/meatball2/47616636</a><br />\n<br />\nB. 形式：<br />\n各大關口、購物熱點（上水、旺角、西九高鐵等）<br />\n連儂牆文宣（各區區議會亦應盡快設定好連儂墻，保障文宣手足安全！）、傳單、街站（大大聲普通話講比大陸人聽）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJ3idBa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJ3idBa.jpg&h=bcc6d841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29wGVPx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29wGVPx.jpg&h=89a68a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AKJqC2T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAKJqC2T.png&h=ef0fff20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76e3e7d15a13d15028c26afbf670885b71ff0255","tid":1835014,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534c194e350a6d2a22ac7ab3cb4c91d46ce6ab3c","tid":1835014,"uid":283587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:57:37.000Z","msg":"而家高鐵外圍啲水馬好似比1-2個月前更多，以前B出口附近無水馬，而家都有埋水馬。<br />\n<br />\n如果可以有方法令好多🐶長期係高鐵附近防守（不論內外）就好，令佢地長期感受愛國同胞的熱情"},{"pid":"6b0bd6ebe3e533c9fad484c9e029040150819153","tid":1835014,"uid":38301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:58:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">年卅晚<br />\n圍高鐵</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d9cebeccb10fbae6dc1ee63b14da62781bc24e41","tid":1835014,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T17:10:48.000Z","msg":"PIN呢個啦:<br />\n以宜家個實力去叫人出黎, 叫唔郁<br />\n上次19號得15萬人<br />\n<br />\n唯一一樣野, 就係搵全港民選嘅區議員出黎, 搞個聯合行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全港區議員出黎，正面要求政府封關，幫手推<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eMyzuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eMyzuS</a>"}]}